ML - automatically learn and improve from experience without being explicitly programmed
Even the best AI will fail if it doesn’t provide unique value to users
Solve a real problem in ways in which AI adds unique value
Shift your thinking from technology-first to people-first

Google aspires to create technologies that solve important problems and help people in their daily lives.
AI technologies will be subject to appropriate human direction and control

Test, Test, Test
Continue to monitor and update the system after deployment

Augmentation versus automation

Who are your users?
What are their values?
Which problem should you solve for them?
How will you solve that problem?
How will you know when the experience is “done”?

